
                    ReSizeable RAMDisk registration


PRIVATE USERS

        Individual users using SRDISK 1.42 on their privately owned
        computers for noncommercial purposes may use it free of charge.


SITE LICENSES

        Business and corporate users are licensed to evaluate SRDISK for
        one month free of charge. After that they are required to buy a
        license for their use of SRDISK.

        The cost of SRDISK for business and corporate users depends on
        the number of computers they license SRDISK for. A minimum
        payment of US$24, equal to two licenses, is required.

        These prices are valid to the end of year 1992; I will propably
        raise them when the version 2.0 is out and proved reliable. Note
        that you can get a discount by registering now.

